Classic load balancer

it helps to distribute the incoming traffic with instances

steps 
	1. create 2 and more instance with html page and security group http
	2. load balance --> select classic load balance 
		--> assign name
		--> Enable advance vpc configuration
		--> select 2 subnet (availability zone)
		--> assign security group
		--> configure heath check
		--> add instances 
		--> add tags
		--> create
